Class TranspositionTable

java.lang.Object
islands.model.player.student.TranspositionTable
public class TranspositionTable extends Object
A table for storing and retrieving the results of calls to SimulatedGameTreePlayer.getMyMove(GameModel, int, islands.model.TileColor).
